| configobj (Python) | 7.8M/mo, 396 dependents, explicitly "not actively maintained" on GitHub, 58 issues, 13 PRs. Nested INI config with validation. No drop-in (configparser lacks nested sections/validation/comment preservation). Medium-large scope (~2,500 LOC). |
| text-unidecode (Python) | 62.3M/mo, single maintainer abandoned since 2019, last commit 2021. Borderline: Unidecode is GPL-only drop-in replacement. Only viable if GPL licensing gap is considered. Very small scope (data tables + lookup). |

